{"tid":2398732,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"喜馬拉雅山冰河崩裂  洪流衝擊印度水壩恐釀150死","createTime":"2021-02-07T14:16:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T00:16:04.000Z","uid":310867,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"585ec0882752cb11ba75deea6da8bdd9aaac7030","tid":2398732,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T14:16:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/licypriyak/status/1358318430940585987?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flicypriyak%2Fstatus%2F1358318430940585987%3Fs%3D21&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOQKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=777f5041\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flicypriyak%2Fstatus%2F1358318430940585987%3Fs%3D21&h=f33769e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/licypriyak/status/1358318430940585987?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/licypriyak/status/1358319779229036544?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flicypriyak%2Fstatus%2F1358319779229036544%3Fs%3D21&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOQKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=c0b48033\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flicypriyak%2Fstatus%2F1358319779229036544%3Fs%3D21&h=7f19959a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/licypriyak/status/1358319779229036544?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n（中央社新德里7日綜合外電報導）喜馬拉雅山冰河今天早上崩裂掉落河裡，激起洪流衝擊印度一座水壩，並摧毀橋梁和道路，恐怕造成高達150人死亡，洪水迫使下游村莊居民撤離。<br />\n<br />\n法新社引述當地媒體報導，意外發生地印度北阿坎德省（Uttarakhand）一座發電廠約有150名員工恐怕被洪水沖走，但當局沒有立即證實這個消息。<br />\n<br />\n北阿坎德省主任秘書普拉卡希（Om Prakash）說，「實際（傷亡）數字尚未證實」，但恐怕有100至150人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n目擊者表示，當大水咆哮著衝下河谷時，他看到一堵由沙土、岩石和水形成的牆。<br />\n<br />\n靠近喜馬拉雅山的印度北阿坎德省容易發生暴洪和山崩。2013年6月創紀錄的降雨導致毀滅性洪水，奪走近6000人性命。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202102070160.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202102070160.aspx&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOQKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=cf93230f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202102070160.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"b34d579b2d339bec712ff075d590b985a368aa72","tid":2398732,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T14:17:56.000Z","msg":"陰功"},{"pid":"f2767ed55f6716a3c6bfa5e44ae8eedb5555fb7a","tid":2398732,"uid":310867,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T14:18:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t7KPTfC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft7KPTfC.png&h=a031be27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64911cec764bbd7f391f71fec68336993238f4cb","tid":2398732,"uid":144541,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T14:19:26.000Z","msg":"又話支那水災好嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解去左印度"},{"pid":"e8340c412338a3ddc69a22c7d53b54fd634a010c","tid":2398732,"uid":293518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T14:21:03.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"826c5835c2eb6779f0652ab106d3229d238d8e85","tid":2398732,"uid":310867,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T14:21:10.000Z","msg":"「印度時報」（The Times of India）報導，印度與西藏邊境警察部隊（Indo-Tibetan Border Police，ITBP）表示，他們已在印度國家火力發電公司（NTPC）位於塔波萬的場址附近，尋獲約9至10人的遺體。<br />\n<br />\n同時根據最新消息，ITBP也已將受困塔波萬附近隧道內的16人全數救出。<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/itbp_official/status/1358408042014859272?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fitbp_official%2Fstatus%2F1358408042014859272%3Fs%3D21&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOQKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=4e39a5c7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fitbp_official%2Fstatus%2F1358408042014859272%3Fs%3D21&h=42d55bec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/itbp_